description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD (101)   
Date: Saturday 28th December 2013

Gaby Logan introduces highlights of six Premier League matches. Defending champions Manchester United make the trip to Carrow Road to face Norwich, in a fixture won by the home side last season. Manchester City host struggling Crystal Palace, while Cardiff meet Sunderland, Swansea travel to Aston Villa, Fulham visit Hull and West Ham take on West Brom.
